{"type":"message","id":"84256f46","parentId":"734ab05d","timestamp":"2026-04-29T03:46:07.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以帮，但我这边现在没法直接操作你的飞牛 Docker。\n\n当前卡点很明确：\n- 我访问 Docker daemon 时被拒绝了\n- 连 `docker ps` 和 `docker inspect gpt_image_playground` 都拿不到权限\n\n你现在在飞牛机器上执行下面这组命令，把输出发我，我就能继续给你精确升级步骤：\n\n```bash\ndocker ps --format 'table {{.Names}}\\t{{.Image}}\\t{{.Status}}' | grep gpt_image_playground\ndocker inspect gpt_image_playground --format '{{.Config.Image}}'\ndocker inspect gpt_image_playground --format '{{json .Mounts}}'\n```\n\n如果你想直接先自己升，通常是这条路线：\n\n```bash\ndocker pull ghcr.io/cooksleep/gpt_image_playground:v0.2.18\ndocker stop gpt_image_playground\ndocker rm gpt_image_playground\n# 然后用你原来的参数重新 docker run\n```\n\n但先别盲删，因为我还没拿到它当前的：\n- 镜像名\n- 挂载目录\n- 端口\n- 环境变量\n\n你把上面 3 条输出给我，我直接帮你拼成一条可执行的升级命令。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f45f0e8b7c4bda50169f17efa33208190915a0cc32ff87665\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":709,"output":282,"cacheRead":31744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32735,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777434354488,"responseId":"resp_0f45f0e8b7c4bda50169f17ef94f288190815e2e68225eeda3"}}
